The '''clone military education complex''' of [[Tipoca City/Legends|Tipoca City]], also known as the '''Kaminoan Military Complex''', was the largest [[Cloning/Legends|clone]] training center on [[Kamino/Legends|Kamino]]. This facility was used to train the [[Clone trooper/Legends|clone troopers]] of the [[Grand Army of the Republic/Legends|Grand Army of the Republic]] prior to and during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]].

==Layout==
[[File:Tipoca_City_Military_Complex_arena.png|thumb|left|240px|The [[Citadel Challenge/Legends|Citadel Challenge]] combat training arena]]

The clone military education complex was located within one of the outer, domed hubs of Tipoca City, and dominated much of the settlement.<ref name="Star Wars: Complete Locations">[[Star Wars: Complete Locations (2005)|''Star Wars: Complete Locations'']]</ref> The innermost chambers housed command centers for [[Kaminoan/Legends|Kaminoan]] supervisors, officials, and scientists. Docks and monitoring stations for the [[KE-8 Enforcer Ship/Legends|KE-8 Enforcers]] and [[Observation Ship/Legends|Observation Ships]] were located nearby.<ref name="Star Wars: Complete Locations" />

The complex itself contained learning and training areas, as well as simulated battlefields. The floor of the upper training levels could be lowered and raised to create various combat (primarily hand-to-hand) training areas, and certain areas could even be made into stadiums for the demonstration of combat skills.<ref name="Star Wars: Complete Locations" /> The large battlefield simulation rooms could replicate a variety of environments and terrains through the use of repulsor floor plates, wind generators, and atmosphere generators.<ref name="Star Wars: Complete Locations" /> Academies for advanced clone units, sleeping and recreational quarters, automated kitchens, assembly areas, dining halls, and even a secret [[Advanced Recon Commando/Legends|ARC Trooper]] training center also existed.<ref name="Star Wars: Complete Locations" /> An egress to the hangars contained transports ready to carry the clones off into the wider [[The galaxy/Legends|galaxy]].

